*pûr'shən, /ˈpɜː(r)ʃən/, /<tt>"p3:(r)S@n</tt>/

===Noun===
'''Persian''' ([[Persians]])

# a person from [[Persia]] (now [[Iran]]) or of Persian descent.
# a speaker of the Persian language.
# a family of languages spoken in Persia, Afghanistan, Tajikistan, parts of Uzbekistan etc. 

